name: Real Enterprise Solutions Development
overview:
RES Software B.V. develops user workspace management software. The company offers RES PowerFuse, an user workspace management solution that enables information technology (IT) professionals to compose and manage a personalized and secure workspace for users. Its RES PowerFuse editions include Platinum Edition, a total management package for Windows platforms; Enterprise Edition, which offers workspace management solutions, including security and performance management, access control, and support; and Standard Edition that manages, automates, and delivers desktops for various users. The company also provides RES Wisdom, a run book automation software for Windows that enables IT professionals to deliver various set of changes to Microsoft Windows environments and automates provisioning of IT resources. In addition, it offers training and online support services. The company provides its solutions to government, healthcare, and education markets in the Netherlands and internationally. It offers its products via the channel and partner network.

The company was founded in 1999 and is based in ‘s-Hertogenbosch, the Netherlands with additional offices in the Netherlands, Norway, Denmark, and the United States. RES Software B.V. is a former subsidiary of RealDolmen NV.
